name: BMO U.S. Equity Value MFR Fund
longDescription: The fund investing primarily in equity securities of U.S. companies priced below their intrinsic value. The Fund follows a disciplined multi-factor security analysis to identify value companies based on fundamental ratios and trading statistics This funds objective is to provide longterm capital growth.
